there's something I must do.

12
00:02:56,043 --> 00:03:00,647
My job isn't done yet.

13
00:03:00,681 --> 00:03:03,517
SAKURA (VOICEOVER): So this
is what she was talking about.

14
00:03:11,058 --> 00:03:13,160
-Is that?

15
00:03:13,193 --> 00:03:14,361
KAKASHI: Yeah.

16
00:03:14,394 --> 00:03:15,529
-Leave him alone, will you?

17
00:03:15,529 --> 00:03:17,064
What do you think you're doing?

18
00:03:24,638 --> 00:03:26,373
SAKURA (VOICEOVER):
Lady Chiyo is

19
00:03:26,373 --> 00:03:28,275
