28
00:04:12,652 --> 00:04:13,286
-Wait.

29
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,554
Are you serious?

30
00:04:14,588 --> 00:04:16,323
NEJI (VOICEOVER): Such
a convenient jutsu

