should not be possible.

32
00:04:20,060 --> 00:04:23,263
That chakra flow.

33
00:04:23,263 --> 00:04:25,132
There's no question.

34
00:04:25,165 --> 00:04:28,368
KAKASHI (VOICEOVER): It
comes at a considerable risk.

35
00:04:28,401 --> 00:04:30,971
[groan]

36
00:04:55,128 --> 00:04:56,329
-Not enough chakra.

37
00:05:04,104 --> 00:05:06,406
[panting]

38
00:05:16,483 --> 00:05:17,250
Come on.

39
00:05:37,237 --> 00:05:39,139
-You can use my chakra.

40
00:05:39,172 --> 00:05:41,374
Take as much as you need to.

41
00:05:41,408 --> 00:05:43,643
That'll work, won't it, Granny?

42
00:05:43,677 --> 00:05:44,611
Please?

43
00:05:44,644 --> 00:05:48,381
[panting]

44
00:05:48,415 --> 00:05:51,618
KAKASHI: Naruto and Gaara
are both jinchuriki.

45
00:05:51,651 --> 00:05:55,088
Naruto knows how Gaara feels
better than anyone in the Sand

46
00:05:55,121 --> 00:05:56,256
ever could.

47
00:05:56,256 --> 00:05:58,091
After all, those
who are jinchuriki

48
