78
00:08:53,633 --> 00:08:58,104
So few women possess
such strong spirit.

79
00:08:58,104 --> 00:09:02,042
You'll surpass your
master as a kunoichi.

80
00:09:02,075 --> 00:09:03,243
I've little doubt.

81
00:09:09,582 --> 00:09:15,588
Naruto, do an old woman
a favor, will you?

82
00:09:15,622 --> 00:09:19,526
You are the only
person in the world

83
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:24,531
who knows the extent
of Gaara's pain.

84
00:09:24,564 --> 00:09:28,368
He also knows your pain.

85
00:09:28,368 --> 00:09:32,338
Please, look after Gaara.

86
00:09:57,497 --> 00:09:58,098
-Gaara.

87
00:10:04,404 --> 00:10:04,971
Gaara!

88
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:10,543
GAARA: Who is that?

89
00:10:10,577 --> 00:10:16,349
