90
00:10:16,382 --> 00:10:17,217
Who is it?

91
00:10:20,220 --> 00:10:20,987
This hand.

92
00:10:24,023 --> 00:10:26,726
Oh.

93
00:10:26,759 --> 00:10:30,497
It's just my hand again.

94
00:10:30,530 --> 00:10:36,336
My hand-- me.

95
00:10:39,239 --> 00:10:42,108
Who am I?

96
00:10:42,108 --> 00:10:48,448
I-- I am--

97
00:10:55,989 --> 00:10:57,247
-Gaara.

98
00:11:04,697 --> 00:11:05,265
-Naruto.

99
00:11:24,184 --> 00:11:26,519
What is this?

100
