-They all came
running to help you.

101
00:11:29,255 --> 00:11:31,591
You've had everyone
worried half to death.

102
00:11:31,624 --> 00:11:33,193
-Lord Gaara!

103
00:11:33,226 --> 00:11:35,128
Sir, are you all right?

104
00:11:42,435 --> 00:11:43,002
Yeah!

105
00:11:43,036 --> 00:11:45,371
[cheering]

106
00:11:45,405 --> 00:11:46,973
Welcome back, sir!

107
00:12:02,488 --> 00:12:05,158
-You sure had us worried there.

108
00:12:05,191 --> 00:12:06,426
-No kidding.

109
00:12:06,459 --> 00:12:09,128
You caused us a whole ton of
grief there, little brother.

110
00:12:09,128 --> 00:12:10,163
-Ugh.

111
00:12:10,196 --> 00:12:12,398
Will you two quit
putting on airs already?

112
00:12:12,398 --> 00:12:14,701
Gaara's the Kazekage, Remember?

113
00:12:14,734 --> 00:12:16,469
Ugh.

114
00:12:16,502 --> 00:12:18,972
Show a little
respect, you nitwits.

115
00:12:21,708 --> 00:12:23,276
-Gaara, talk to me.

116
00:12:23,309 --> 00:12:24,110
How do you feel?

117
00:12:32,485 --> 00:12:33,453
-Easy.

118
00:12:33,486 --> 00:12:35,288
You shouldn't get
up too quickly.

119
00:12:35,321 --> 00:12:37,690
Your body hasn't completely
recovered from the rigor mortis

120
00:12:37,724 --> 00:12:38,291
yet.

121
00:12:42,128 --> 00:12:42,695
-Oh.

122
00:12:42,729 --> 00:12:43,997
Thanks be to the heavens!

123
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:45,665
I thought we'd lost him.

124
00:12:45,665 --> 00:12:48,334
Without the Lord Kazekage I'd--

125
00:12:48,368 --> 00:12:50,103
-Get a hold of yourself.

126
00:12:50,103 --> 00:12:52,438
There's no way we'd
ever lose Lord Gaara.

127
00:12:52,472 --> 00:12:54,974
Lord Gaara is the
hottest thing ever.

128
00:12:55,008 --> 00:12:57,210
He's a quiet, cool,
strong, and elite warrior.

129
00:12:57,243 --> 00:12:58,278
-Yeah.

130
00:12:58,311 --> 00:13:00,647
