gorgeous, isn't he?

131
00:13:00,680 --> 00:13:02,615
After all, he is Kazekage.

132
00:13:02,649 --> 00:13:04,250
-If anything should
ever happen again,

133
00:13:04,284 --> 00:13:06,386
I'll protect him
with all my heart.

134
00:13:06,386 --> 00:13:06,986
-No.

135
00:13:06,986 --> 00:13:07,654
I will!

136
00:13:07,687 --> 00:13:09,088
-Get in line.

137
00:13:09,122 --> 00:13:10,920
-Lord Gaara!

138
00:13:15,194 --> 00:13:17,497
-I know I'm still a genin
and all, but come on.

139
00:13:17,530 --> 00:13:19,532
Cut me a break.

140
00:13:19,565 --> 00:13:22,368
KANKURO: Ah, don't sweat it.

141
00:13:22,402 --> 00:13:24,470
Women always go
weak in the knees

142
00:13:24,504 --> 00:13:27,040
for that cool,
elite type of guy.

143
00:13:27,073 --> 00:13:28,107
So what can you do?

144
00:13:28,141 --> 00:13:29,642
Am I right?

145
00:13:29,642 --> 00:13:33,646
-I'm pretty sure Shikamaru said
something like that once too.

146
00:13:37,684 --> 00:13:40,420
GAARA: He's known
the same pain I have,

147
00:13:40,453 --> 00:13:43,623
and he taught me
that I can change

148
00:13:43,656 --> 00:13:47,193
the path my life will follow.

149
00:13:47,226 --> 00:13:51,397
One day, Kankuro, I'd like
to become something precious

150
00:13:51,397 --> 00:13:52,332
to others too.

151
00:13:58,738 --> 00:14:01,574
KANKURO: Naruto, thank you.

152
00:14:01,607 --> 00:14:03,509
-Huh?

153
00:14:03,543 --> 00:14:04,243
Hey.

154
00:14:04,243 --> 00:14:05,411
Don't look at me.

155
00:14:05,445 --> 00:14:08,214
It's granny over there that
you should be thanking.

156
00:14:08,247 --> 00:14:11,384
She saved Gaara with some kind
of incredible Medical Ninjutsu.

157
00:14:18,458 --> 00:14:21,160
She tired herself
out and fell asleep,

158
00:14:21,194 --> 00:14:24,836
but I'm sure she'll be fine when
we get her back to the village.

159
00:14:24,932 --> 00:14:25,951
KANKURO: No. She won't.

160
00:14:36,175 --> 00:14:39,645
Granny Chiyo used "that" jutsu.

161
00:14:39,645 --> 00:14:41,514
-What are you talking about?

162
00:14:41,514 --> 00:14:42,148
Why won't she?

163
00:14:47,253 --> 00:14:49,055
-I will.

164
00:14:49,088 --> 00:14:49,989
-Huh?

165
00:14:49,989 --> 00:14:51,057
-Huh?

166
00:14:51,090 --> 00:14:53,459
KANKURO: She wasn't
using Medical Ninjutsu.

167
00:14:53,493 --> 00:14:55,561
It was a Reanimation Ninjutsu.

168
00:14:59,232 --> 00:15:01,501
Granny Chiyo is dead.

169
00:15:05,538 --> 00:15:06,572
-Reanimation Jutsu?

170
00:15:09,108 --> 00:15:09,976
-What are you saying?

171
00:15:10,009 --> 00:15:12,011
How can she be dead?

172
00:15:12,044 --> 00:15:14,380
-It's a ninjutsu that allows
you to bring someone back

173
00:15:14,380 --> 00:15:18,518
from the dead in exchange
for your own life.

174
00:15:18,551 --> 00:15:21,521
-It can't be.

175
00:15:21,554 --> 00:15:23,222
NEJI (VOICEOVER): As I thought.

176
00:15:23,256 --> 00:15:24,524
-Guy-sensei.

177
00:15:24,557 --> 00:15:25,124
-Mm.

178
00:15:31,330 --> 00:15:34,634
-Years ago, in our
Puppet Master corps,

179
00:15:34,667 --> 00:15:37,336
a jutsu was secretly
developed to breathe life

180
00:15:37,370 --> 00:15:40,106
into actual puppets.

181
00:15:40,106 --> 00:15:42,008
Granny Chiyo led that project.

182
00:15:45,178 --> 00:15:49,515
They did come up with a
method for it, however,

183
00:15:49,515 --> 00:15:52,618
midway they concluded there
was too much risk involved.

184
00:15:52,652 --> 00:15:54,754
It was classified
as forbidden jutsu

185
00:15:54,987 --> 00:15:58,057
before human testing could
be done, and sealed away.

186
00:16:02,428 --> 00:16:04,997
CHIYO: In this world
of shinobi created

187
00:16:05,031 --> 00:16:08,701
by frivolous old people,
it's a great comfort

188
00:16:08,734 --> 00:16:13,105
to know that new souls like
yourself have come along.

189
00:16:13,105 --> 00:16:19,078
Up till now, everything I've
done in my life has been wrong.

190
00:16:19,111 --> 00:16:22,482
But at least here
in my final hour

191
00:16:22,515 --> 00:16:26,552
I can finally do something
right for a change.

192
00:16:26,586 --> 00:16:31,090
The Sand and the Leaf, may
the future that awaits them

193
00:16:31,123 --> 00:16:34,026
be different from the way
things were in our time.

194
00:16:36,996 --> 00:16:41,667
This special power of yours
that Kakashi spoke of,

195
00:16:41,701 --> 00:16:45,104
that power will change
the future dramatically.

196
00:16:50,476 --> 00:16:55,381
Become a Hokage the likes of
