like this for Gaara.

212
00:18:26,639 --> 00:18:31,410
KAKASHI: Lady Chiyo entrusted
the future to you and Gaara.

213
00:18:31,444 --> 00:18:34,580
It was a death
befitting a shinobi.

214
00:18:39,518 --> 00:18:41,020
-Yeah.

215
00:18:41,053 --> 00:18:44,657
Just like the Third.

216
00:18:44,657 --> 00:18:45,658
-That's true.

217
00:18:48,661 --> 00:18:49,295
-Hm.

218
00:18:49,328 --> 00:18:51,631
I get it now.

219
00:18:51,664 --> 00:18:55,301
I understand what
Granny wished for.

220
00:18:55,334 --> 00:18:57,269
-Lord Gaara, are you all right?

221
00:18:57,303 --> 00:18:58,270
-I'm fine.

222
00:19:39,545 --> 00:19:44,383
Everyone, pray for Lady
Chiyo, and bid her farewell.

223
00:20:09,442 --> 00:20:10,643
SAKURA (VOICEOVER): Lady Chiyo.

