chunin exams in the Leaf.

246
00:22:51,683 --> 00:22:53,585
TEMARI: Can you believe
it's been three years?

247
00:22:53,619 --> 00:22:55,654
KANKURO: That's when
Gaara flipped out and went

248
00:22:55,654 --> 00:22:58,257
